{"tid":1807365,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"民權觀察稱3名觀察員在元旦遊行後被捕","createTime":"2020-01-01T18:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T13:31:48.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f9fe612e5864f5119a19161d1c42cfb9daa77d94","tid":1807365,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:53:01.000Z","msg":"民權觀察發表聲明，指有三名觀察員在元旦遊行後被捕，強烈譴責警方濫捕並要求立即釋放三人。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察在聲明指出，該三名觀察員在崇光百貨對開被警方防線圍困，等候數小時後被拘捕，是組織自2018年成立觀察員團隊以來，首次有觀察員被捕，但是在過去半年，觀察員一直可以順利記錄警方的行動，並曾進入警察的封鎖線內了解示威者被捕或抬走的情況。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察譴責警方無理拘捕，違反人權標準、保障見解自由及言論自由的責任，又表示強烈關注警方於元旦在銅鑼灣的圍捕行動，質疑警方企圖以大規模濫捕的方式，阻嚇和平示威者行使集會及表達意見的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500581-20200102.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500581-20200102.htm&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAP2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=69e8fadb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500581-20200102.htm&h=1f572207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500581-20200102.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d314159a1ab7a7a018d42288e3f1913b9ef81dd9","tid":1807365,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eddd88dd5d69985e85ec5fea589f822656200ea6","tid":1807365,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T18:55:41.000Z","msg":"【旺角狗倒地真相！！】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1807368\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1807368</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8e131e31ae1034fd7f3d2ef00fc5f9c